org.apache.paimon.append

Class AppendOnlyWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.paimon.append.AppendOnlyWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MemoryOwner, BatchRecordWriter, RecordWriter<InternalRow>

    public class AppendOnlyWriter
extends Object
implements BatchRecordWriter, MemoryOwner
    A RecordWriter implementation that only accepts records which are always insert operations and don't have any unique keys or sort keys.
